recommended_for_you.title: Recommended
recommended_for_you.description: We picked these out just for you.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

522072.title: Silent Hill
522072.description: A mother desperately searches for her adopted daughter through a town that’s been possessed by an evil force. Can she find her in time?

528599.title: Takers
528599.description: High-octane thriller about a group of notorious criminals whose streak of untraceable bank heists may come to an end thanks to a hardcore detective.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

539274.title: The Glass House
539274.description: When Ruby and her brother are orphaned after a family tragedy, they're taken in by family friends. Until it becomes clear that something is wrong.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

559020.title: Terrifier
559020.description: A maniacal clown uses gruesome methods to viciously torture and murder women who have the unfortunate luck of entering his house of horrors.

563168.title: Predators
563168.description: A mercenary reluctantly leads a group of elite warriors mysteriously brought together on a jungle planet where they are hunted by an alien race.

571078.title: Obsessed
571078.description: A happily married businessman finds his life in shambles after a woman pursues him relentlessly, putting his wife in a dangerous predicament.

588416.title: 13 Assassins (Dubbed)
588416.description: Incredible action sequences mark this thrilling tale of an elite samurai force who get assigned a secret mission to take down a sadistic overlord.

590740.title: The Man From Nowhere (English Dubbed)
590740.description: An ex-enforcer sets aside his new and quietly humble life to take on a brutal trafficking ring to keep a child, his only friend, from harm’s way.

591015.title: Proud Mary
591015.description: Taraji P. Henson stars as a steely hit woman working for a local Mob family who finds a protective instinct for a little boy while out for a kill.

591107.title: The House Bunny
591107.description: A former Playboy model finds a new path in life when she becomes an unlikely mentor and role model to a sorority full of studious young college students.

592664.title: The Miracle Season
592664.description: After their star player dies, a bereaved girl and tenacious coach lead their school volleyball team and town to victory, in this moving true story.

593866.title: Baby Boy
593866.description: The classic John Singleton film about a 20-year-old in South Central L.A. who loves like a man but isn’t stepping up in real life as a grown adult.

595396.description: Tells the story of how Spartan King Leonidas and his soldiers numbering just 300 beat King Xerxes of Persia, with an army of hundreds of thousands.

610572.title: Goodfellas
610572.description: Based on a true story, a young man rises up the ranks of a mob family over several years, dabbling in drugs, heists and murders along the way.

616504.title: Bring It On: Again
616504.description: In this sassy sequel, a new squad of cheerleaders takes on the establishment in a winner-takes-all competition filled with spunk, smarts and spirit.

616506.title: Bring It On: In It to Win It
616506.description: Hot music, high-flyin' fun and no-holds-barred competition reach new heights when the East Coast Jets take on their rivals, the West Coast Sharks!

616510.title: Bring It On: Fight to the Finish
616510.description: Get ready for more hot music, fierce competition and high-flyin’ fun in Bring It On: Fight to the Finish starring Christina Milian.

616516.title: Bring It On: All or Nothing
616516.description: When a popular cheerleader moves from her posh neighborhood to a working-class one, she soon finds herself at odds with her new classmates.

617284.title: A Low Down Dirty Shame
617284.description: A disgraced LAPD cop-turned private eye teams up with a DEA agent in a search for $20 million in stolen cash and the drug kingpin who ended his career.

625256.title: First Sunday
625256.description: Two bumbling criminals discover they haven't got a prayer when they attempt to steal from the local church.

625717.title: Phat Girlz
625717.description: Oscar winner Mo’Nique stars as a fashion designer ready to bring her plus-size clothing line to the mainstream, despite financial challenges.

630919.title: Major Payne
630919.description: In peacetime, a major with a lust for war is discharged from the Marine Corps and reduced to training a group of misfit ROTC cadets at a prep school.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

663215.title: How High
663215.description: Silas and Jamal are two slackers who beat the odds and get accepted to Harvard, where they turn the school upside down with their pursuit of parties.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

664191.title: Double Take
664191.description: An investment banker on the run swipes the passport of a petty thief, thus swapping identities, in this comic urban take on the Prince and the Pauper.

667422.title: Pacific Rim
667422.description: With alien invaders rising from the sea, a washed-up former pilot and an untested trainee use massive robots to combat the apocalyptic threat.

675608.title: Saban's Power Rangers
675608.description: Five ordinary teenagers must team together to become something extraordinary in order to save the world from being obliterated by an alien threat.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

686287.title: Honey 4: Rise Up and Dance
686287.description: A street dancer comes out of the shadow of her trained dancer sister and enters a dance competition with the prize being a college scholarship.

698742.title: Bed Rest
698742.description: After struggling to start a family, Julie Rivers is pregnant again. Put on mandatory bed rest, Julie starts unraveling as ghostly experiences in the home begin closing in on her.

698980.title: Dead Silence
698980.description: After the murder of his wife, a man returns to his hometown and uncovers the terrifying legend of Mary Shaw, a cursed ventriloquist from the 40s.

707513.title: Big Stan
707513.description: Panicked he’ll be defenseless in prison, a gutless con man sentenced to hard time for fraud gets 11th hour training from a martial arts master.

711197.title: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
711197.description: A comically penned love letter to 1990’s urban films that follows the eventful life of a teen boy and his crew after he moves into his father’s ‘hood.

712225.title: Jeepers Creepers 2
712225.description: When their bus breaks down on a deserted road, a team of high school athletes discovers an opponent they cannot defeat and may not survive.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

714940.title: Secret Society 2: Never Enough
714940.description: Celess is back with a newfound hunger and a bestie on the brink of making it big only to learn that the bigger you become, the harder you fall.

720947.title: Little Man
720947.description: After a stolen diamond gets stashed in the home of a husband and wife, a pint-sized jewel thief poses as the world's ugliest baby to get it back.

723256.title: Red Sparrow
723256.description: A Russian intelligence officer tasked with seducing a CIA agent finds her mission and its objective threatened when they both fall for each other.

100000194.title: I Got the Hook-Up 2
100000194.description: After a health inspector threatens to shut down a restaurant, young hustlers Fatboy and Spyda attempt to pull off a scam to save it from closure.

100000320.title: Taken 2
100000320.description: When retired CIA operative Brian Mills and his wife are taken hostage by a vengeful gang leader, they must rely on their daughter's help to escape.

100000480.title: Bad Teacher
100000480.description: A foul-mouthed seventh grade teacher begrudgingly returns to work so that she can pay for breast implants after being dumped by her sugar daddy.

100000719.title: Surprise
100000719.description: Convinced his wife is cheating on him with his best friend, a husband goes off the deep end into a conspiracy, only to find himself unprepared for what comes next.

100000965.title: A Good Man
100000965.description: Struggling in the aftermath of his wife's affair, a man's attempt at a new relationship begins to spiral out of control when he notices familiar signs.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001725.title: Mindcage
100001725.description: Two detectives must strike a deal with a brilliant serial killer on death row who turned his victims into art exhibits when a copycat killer strikes.

100001935.title: The Predator
100001935.description: When a young boy accidentally sparks a battle with genetically-enhanced aliens, a ragtag crew of ex-Marines bands together to save the human race.

100001992.title: Illegal Tender
100001992.description: When his family's shadowy past comes back to haunt them, a college student learns the dark source of their wealth and fights off their enemies.

100001993.title: Hanna
100001993.description: Raised in isolation by her father to be the perfect assassin, 16-year-old Hanna sets out on a mission to kill a merciless CIA operative.

100002047.title: Bring It On
100002047.description: With national championships fast approaching, the new cheerleading captain discovers that their winning routines were stolen from a rival squad.

100002155.title: A Body to Kill For
100002155.description: Growing up in Philadelphia, China enjoys a life of privilege until a handsome suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that changes her forever.

100002351.title: The Bourne Identity
100002351.description: An elite government agent is pulled out of a fishing boat with two bullets in his back and no memory before being forced on the run from assassins.

100002566.title: Watch Your Back
100002566.description: As one of Detroit's top strippers, Kanisha effortlessly seduces and manipulates men out of their money to fund her extravagant lifestyle.

100002888.description: An academic researcher opens a portal into a parallel universe and makes contact with his double in order to prevent an apocalypse.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

04294.title: Dance Moms
04294.description: Popular reality series following the tough love teaching by a dance instructor-choreographer of talented tweens and her occasional parental run-ins.

0300008167.title: Bad Girls Club
0300008167.description: A group of women with anger and control issues come together and try to improve themselves. But moving forward isn’t going to be easy.

0300009519.title: Spook Show 17
0300009519.description: An innovator makes his own reality TV show about how he and his wife led a crew to build the craziest, most elaborate haunted house in the galaxy.

01627.title: Hunter X Hunter (English Subtitle)
01627.description: A young boy, who dreams of being a hunter like his father, must pass the notoriously difficult and dangerous Hunter Qualification Exam.

0300000080.title: The Book of Negroes
0300000080.description: Kidnapped in Africa and enslaved in South Carolina as a girl, a woman attempts to secure her freedom in eighteenth century North America.

0300010082.title: Third Watch
0300010082.description: A drama about the brave and dedicated people who serve as paramedics, firefighters, and police on the “third watch,” the 3:00 PM to 11:00 PM shift.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

0300009077.title: The Temptations
0300009077.description: One of Motown's most successful vocal acts was forced to battle prejudice, betrayal, drug abuse and more to become R&B and soul music royalty.

0300009344.title: MasterChef
0300009344.description: Returning contestants vie for the top prize as MasterChef reopens its doors to some of the most memorable cooks in the competition’s history.

0300009219.title: Quantico
0300009219.description: FBI recruits form friendships while training at Quantico Base. But relationships are tested when one of them becomes a suspect in a terrorist attack.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

0300008306.title: Next Level Chef
0300008306.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay hosts ambitious chefs facing unique cooking challenges, in a culinary competition to be the food world’s next superstar.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300000245.title: The Dirty D
0300000245.description: Detroit's hottest nightclub is a world of drugs, sex, and money run by a shady power couple. Here there are no rules, and everyone plays for keeps.

0300006821.title: Ambitions
0300006821.description: Two top Atlanta lawyers compete in personal and professional endeavors, in a battle of ambitions that so often gets out of control.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

0300009178.title: The Dirty D
0300009178.description: Detroit's hottest nightclub is a world of drugs, sex, and money run by a shady power couple. Here there are no rules, and everyone plays for keeps.

0300010238.title: Bad Girls All-Star Battle
0300010238.description: Bad Girls All-Star Battle features fun, over-the-top physical and mental challenges that will test the limits of the world's feistiest ladies.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

03646.title: Little Women: Atlanta
03646.description: There's no shortage of excitement in this circle of friends as they face the daily challenges that come with being a little person in the big city.

0300005163.title: The Masked Singer
0300005163.description: Celebrity performers, costumed to conceal their identities but dropping hints along the way, compete each week as one is eliminated and unmasked.
